<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NSL Click & Work - Student Canvas</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --nsl-red: #cc1f1f;
            --nsl-gold: #f2a900;
            --nsl-dark: #1a1a1a;
            --nsl-light: #f5f5f5;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: #e0e0e0;
            color: var(--nsl-dark);
            -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact !important;
            print-color-adjust: exact !important;
        }
        .page {
            width: 210mm;
            height: 297mm; /* A4 Portrait */
            background: white;
            margin: 20px auto;
            position: relative;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        @media print {
            body { background: white; margin: 0; }
            .page { margin: 0; box-shadow: none; width: 210mm; height: 297mm; page-break-after: always; }
            @page { size: A4 portrait; margin: 0; }
        }
        
        .header {
            background: var(--nsl-dark);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 8px solid var(--nsl-red);
        }
        .header img.logo-nsl {
            height: 60px;
        }
        .header img.logo-text {
            height: 35px;
        }
        h1 { font-size: 38px; font-weight: 900; margin: 0 0 10px 0; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .subtitle { color: var(--nsl-gold); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1px; }

        .content {
            padding: 40px;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Journey Timeline */
        .timeline {
            position: relative;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 30px auto;
        }
        .timeline::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; bottom: 0; left: 30px;
            width: 6px;
            background: var(--nsl-light);
            border-radius: 6px;
        }

        .step {
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            padding-left: 80px;
        }
        .step:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

        .step-number {
            position: absolute;
            left: 10px; top: 0;
            width: 46px; height: 46px;
            background: var(--nsl-dark);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-size: 22px; font-weight: 900;
            border: 4px solid white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            z-index: 2;
        }
        
        .step.active .step-number {
            background: var(--nsl-red);
        }

        .step h3 {
            margin: 0 0 5px 0;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--nsl-dark);
        }
        .step p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .footer {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
            background: var(--nsl-light);
            padding: 30px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 4px solid var(--nsl-gold);
        }

        .usp-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 2px dashed #ccc;
        }
        .usp-item h4 { margin: 0 0 5px 0; color: var(--nsl-red); font-size: 18px; }
        .usp-item p { margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666; }

        .top-controls {
            position: fixed;
            top: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            z-index: 1000;
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .lang-switch { display: flex; gap: 5px; }
        .lang-btn {
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            color: #666;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .lang-btn.active { background: var(--nsl-dark); color: white; }
        .print-btn {
            background: var(--nsl-red); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 5px 15px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; cursor: pointer;
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .print-btn:hover { background: #a11818; }
        @media print { .top-controls { display: none !important; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="top-controls">
        <div class="lang-switch">
            <a href="?lang=en" class="lang-btn <%= lang === 'en' ? 'active' : '' %>">EN</a>
            <a href="?lang=de" class="lang-btn <%= lang === 'de' ? 'active' : '' %>">DE</a>
        </div>
        <button onclick="window.print()" class="print-btn">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 6 2 18 2 18 9"></polyline><path d="M6 18H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v5a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2"></path><rect x="6" y="14" width="12" height="8"></rect></svg>
            PDF / Print
        </button>
    </div>

    <div class="page">
        <div class="header">
            <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; gap: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <img src="/assets/design/NSL_logo_mid.png" alt="NSL Click & Work" class="logo-nsl">
                <img src="/assets/design/Logo_Mid_PersonalKampagne.png" alt="PersonalKampagne" class="logo-text">
            </div>
            <h1>Your Journey to Germany</h1>
            <div class="subtitle">TRANSPARENT. FAST. SECURE.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 40px; color: #444;">
                With the <strong>NSL Click & Work Portal</strong>, you have full control over your application process. Track your progress in real-time and know exactly what steps to take next.
            </p>

            <div class="timeline">
                <div class="step active">
                    <div class="step-number">1</div>
                    <h3>Assessment Test</h3>
                    <p>Complete the comprehensive assessment to evaluate your IQ, decision making, and skills. Get your NSL-Score.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="step active">
                    <div class="step-number" style="background: var(--nsl-gold); color: var(--nsl-dark);">2</div>
                    <h3>Interview & Media</h3>
                    <p>Record your introduction video and take your profile photo. We create a professional "Setcard" (PDF Resume) for you.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">3</div>
                    <h3>Profile Live</h3>
                    <p>Your profile is activated on the portal. German employers and partners can now view your Setcard and Video.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">4</div>
                    <h3>Employer Matching</h3>
                    <p>Congratulations! An employer has selected your profile. You are now in direct consideration for a position.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">5</div>
                    <h3>Contract & Integration</h3>
                    <p>Sign your employment or training contract. Begin your language and integration courses.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">6</div>
                    <h3>Visa & Departure</h3>
                    <p>Complete the visa process and book your flight. Welcome to Germany!</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="usp-grid">
                <div class="usp-item">
                    <h4>📱 Always Updated</h4>
                    <p>Log in with your ID anytime to see your current progress and NSL Score.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="usp-item">
                    <h4>🔒 100% GDPR Secure</h4>
                    <p>Your data is protected under strict European privacy laws. You are in control.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <h3 style="margin: 0 0 5px 0; font-size: 20px;">Ready to start your journey?</h3>
            <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 15px; color: #666;">Ask your local center for details, or login below.</p>
            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 18px;">
                <strong>Student Portal:</strong> <a href="https://www.personalkampagne-portal.de" style="color: var(--nsl-red); text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">www.personalkampagne-portal.de</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
